{"_id":"01b2c2da1b4f69bd","name":"Level 1 Rituals","pages":[{"_id":"9783ef7905b79b83","name":"Level 1 Rituals","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"content":"<h2>Blood Sorcery Rituals — Level 1</h2>\n<h3>Blood Walk</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 1 hour</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A taste of the subject's blood</p><p>By tasting the blood of another Kindred, the caster can determine their generation, clan, sire, and any blood bonds. Provides a vision of the subject's lineage.</p><hr>\n<h3>Clinging of the Insect</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 10 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A living spider, consumed</p><p>Allows the caster to climb and cling to walls and ceilings like a spider for the remainder of the night.</p><hr>\n<h3>Craft Bloodstone</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 3 hours</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A small smooth pebble and a point of vitae</p><p>Enchants a small pebble to glow when within a certain distance of Kindred vitae. Useful for detecting vampires or hidden blood stores.</p><hr>\n<h3>Wake with Evening's Freshness</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 15 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> The caster's vitae spread around the resting place</p><p>Allows the caster to awaken at any sign of danger during the day without the need for a Humanity roll, rising one hour before sunset if undisturbed.</p><hr>\n<h3>Communicate with Kindred Sire</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 30 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> An object once belonging to the sire</p><p>Opens a telepathic channel between the caster and their sire, allowing communication over any distance for a single night. Both parties must be willing.</p><hr>\n<h3>Defence of the Sacred Haven</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 1 hour</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Vitae painted along all window frames and door thresholds</p><p>Wards a single room against sunlight. Any windows or openings are mystically sealed against daylight, though the room becomes pitch black. Lasts until the next sunset.</p><hr>\n<h3>Illuminate the Trail of Prey</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 15 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A personal possession of the target</p><p>By casting this ritual over an object belonging to a person, the caster can see ghostly footprints tracing the owner's recent path. Tracks last until sunrise.</p><hr>\n<h3>Purge the Inner Demon</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 20 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A vial of holy water mixed with vitae</p><p>Grants the caster or a willing target a bonus die to resist frenzy for the remainder of the night. Multiple castings do not stack.</p><hr>","format":1},"sort":0}],"sort":1,"flags":{}}
{"_id":"84944abdc4b20eaa","name":"Level 2 Rituals","pages":[{"_id":"dac9a39720d26772","name":"Level 2 Rituals","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"content":"<h2>Blood Sorcery Rituals — Level 2</h2>\n<h3>Warding Circle vs Ghouls</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 30 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Vitae traced in a circle, salt</p><p>Creates an invisible circle on the ground that no ghoul can willingly cross. Ghouls who attempt to cross suffer aggravated damage. Lasts until the next sunrise.</p><hr>\n<h3>Deflection of Wooden Doom</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 1 hour</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Wood shavings dissolved in vitae, consumed</p><p>Enchants the caster's body so that the first wooden stake that strikes them during the night shatters harmlessly on contact. Single use per casting.</p><hr>\n<h3>Extinguish</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> Instant (1 turn ritual action)</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A vial of water mixed with ash</p><p>Instantly douses all mundane fires within a certain radius. Supernatural fires resist but are reduced. Useful against frenzy triggers.</p><hr>\n<h3>Eyes of Babel</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 30 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A page from a foreign language text, burned and mixed with vitae</p><p>Allows the caster to understand and speak any human language for the remainder of the night. Does not grant literacy.</p><hr>\n<h3>Truth of Blood</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery vs Composure + Subterfuge | <strong>Time:</strong> 5 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A drop of vitae applied to the subject's lips</p><p>By anointing a subject's lips with vitae, the caster compels them to speak only the truth for the next few minutes. Supernaturals may resist.</p><hr>\n<h3>Ward vs Lupines</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 1 hour</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Vitae and silver dust traced on the surface</p><p>Inscribes a mystical ward on a surface that repels werewolves. A Lupine attempting to touch or pass the ward takes 2 Aggravated damage and must roll Willpower (Difficulty 3) to proceed.</p><hr>\n<h3>Herd Whisper</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 10 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A drop of blood from one Herd member</p><p>Allows the caster to speak a short message (one sentence) that all members of their Herd hear telepathically, regardless of distance. They cannot reply. Useful for summoning vessels.</p><hr>","format":1},"sort":0}],"sort":2,"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dd0436f57d5f0856","name":"Level 3 Rituals","pages":[{"_id":"396dd933218c31d4","name":"Level 3 Rituals","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"content":"<h2>Blood Sorcery Rituals — Level 3</h2>\n<h3>Warding Circle vs Kindred</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 1 hour</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Vitae of the caster traced in a circle, bone dust</p><p>Creates an invisible circle that no vampire can willingly cross. Kindred who force their way through suffer aggravated damage. Lasts until sunrise.</p><hr>\n<h3>Firewalker</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 30 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A candle flame extinguished with vitae</p><p>Grants the caster resistance to fire for the remainder of the night. Fire damage is reduced and Rotschreck difficulties are lowered.</p><hr>\n<h3>Incorporeal Passage</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 10 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A shard of mirror smeared with vitae</p><p>Allows the caster to pass through a single solid barrier — wall, door, or floor — as though it were not there. One passage per casting.</p><hr>\n<h3>Pavis of Foul Presence</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 20 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Vitae painted on the caster's forehead (invisible to mortals)</p><p>Wards the caster against Presence powers. Any Presence attempt directed at the caster is reflected back upon the user for the remainder of the scene.</p><hr>\n<h3>Shaft of Belated Quiescence</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 3 nights preparation + 10 minutes casting</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A wooden stake soaked in vitae for three nights</p><p>Enchants a wooden stake so that it splinters inside the target on impact, releasing a paralytic blood magic effect. Even if the heart is missed, the target is immobilized for a time.</p><hr>\n<h3>Vitae Block</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery vs Sta + Resolve | <strong>Time:</strong> 1 turn (combat ritual)</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A drop of the target's vitae (previously acquired)</p><p>Target a Kindred within line of sight. On success, the target cannot use Blood Surge, mend damage, or activate discipline powers requiring Rouse checks for a number of turns equal to successes rolled.</p><hr>\n<h3>Cleansing of the Flesh</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 15 minutes</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Clean water mixed with vitae, poured over the subject</p><p>Purges all mundane toxins, drugs, and diseases from the caster's body or a willing target. Also neutralizes ingested poisons in blood. Does not affect supernatural conditions.</p><hr>","format":1},"sort":0}],"sort":3,"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7bcb3616a73353be","name":"Level 4 Rituals","pages":[{"_id":"c81960fda3d063e5","name":"Level 4 Rituals","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"content":"<h2>Blood Sorcery Rituals — Level 4</h2>\n<h3>Warding Circle vs Spirits</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 1 hour</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Salt, iron filings, and vitae traced in a circle</p><p>Creates an invisible circle that no spirit, ghost, or wraith can cross. Spirits who attempt to breach it suffer damage and are repelled. Lasts until sunrise.</p><hr>\n<h3>Heart of Stone</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 2 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 4 hours</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A carved stone replica of a heart, vitae</p><p>The caster mystically transforms their heart to stone, rendering them immune to staking. Emotions are dulled and social interactions suffer, but the caster is protected from the most feared Kindred vulnerability.</p><hr>\n<h3>Bone of Lies</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 3 hours</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A mortal bone (finger bone or rib), soaked in vitae</p><p>Enchants a mortal bone so that whoever holds it cannot speak a deliberate lie. The holder is compelled toward truth, though they may remain silent. The bone blackens slightly with each lie it prevents.</p><hr>\n<h3>Splinter Servant</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 2 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 2 hours</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A sharpened stake, vitae, a strand of the target's hair</p><p>Animates a wooden stake to fly toward a designated target and attempt to stake them in the heart. The stake acts with a dice pool determined by the caster's ritual successes.</p><hr>\n<h3>Blood Curse</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 2 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery vs Sta + Resolve | <strong>Time:</strong> 3 hours</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A vial of the target's blood, black candles, graveyard dirt</p><p>Curse a target whose blood you possess. The target suffers a 2-die penalty to all rolls for a number of nights equal to your successes. The target feels a persistent sense of dread and misfortune.</p><hr>\n<h3>Mirror of Second Sight</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 1 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 2 hours</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A silver-backed mirror anointed with vitae</p><p>Enchants a mirror to reveal the true nature of anyone reflected in it. Vampires appear as corpses, Lupines appear as wolves, ghosts become visible, and disguises (including Obfuscate) are stripped away. Lasts one night.</p><hr>","format":1},"sort":0}],"sort":4,"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8ab8ea3bf31fd2eb","name":"Level 5 Rituals","pages":[{"_id":"44971883dded5caf","name":"Level 5 Rituals","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"content":"<h2>Blood Sorcery Rituals — Level 5</h2>\n<h3>Escape to a True Friend</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 2 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 3 hours preparation; instant activation</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A lock of hair and a drop of blood from both the caster and the friend, a circle of candles</p><p>In a moment of dire need, the caster is instantly transported to the location of a person they consider a true friend. The caster vanishes and reappears beside this ally, regardless of distance. Can only be used once per lunar cycle.</p><hr>\n<h3>Blood Contract</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 2 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 6 hours</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Vellum made from the skin of an animal sacrificed under a new moon, vitae from all parties</p><p>Creates a mystically binding contract written in vitae. All parties who sign suffer aggravated damage and a curse if they break the terms. The contract burns to ash if fulfilled or if all parties are destroyed.</p><hr>\n<h3>Summon the Departed</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 3 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> 2 hours</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> A personal possession of the deceased, graveyard dirt, vitae, black candles</p><p>Conjures the ghost of a deceased mortal or destroyed Kindred. The spirit is compelled to answer questions honestly for a number of minutes equal to the caster's successes. The spirit may be hostile.</p><hr>\n<h3>Rite of the Last Drink</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 3 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> One full night</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> The caster's own vitae, consecrated soil, a willing sacrifice of 2 Aggravated Health damage</p><p>Enchants the caster's vitae so that any Kindred who commits Diablerie on them suffers catastrophic consequences — the diablerizer's soul is consumed by the victim's instead, effectively destroying the attacker's personality.</p><hr>\n<h3>Ward of the Domain</h3><p><strong>Cost:</strong> 3 Rouse | <strong>Pool:</strong> Int + Blood Sorcery | <strong>Time:</strong> One full night</p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Vitae painted on every entrance, the caster's blood mixed with the foundation's mortar or soil</p><p>Enchants an entire building or estate. Any supernatural being entering without the caster's permission feels intense discomfort and suffers 1 Aggravated Willpower damage per hour. The caster senses all intrusions. Lasts one lunar cycle.</p><hr>","format":1},"sort":0}],"sort":5,"flags":{}}
